{"tid":913102,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"冷冷冷！特朗普：全球變暖是騙局","createTime":"2018-11-23T07:08:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-25T11:50:52.000Z","uid":32938,"like":156,"dislike":48,"uniUserReply":62,"replies":[{"pid":"8498172c68fd7289a90a8176d39536c30ddf37fb","tid":913102,"uid":32938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T07:08:33.000Z","msg":"據美國天氣預報，美國東北部22日將明顯變冷，溫度會低於平時這個季節。為此，美國總統特朗普在推特上寫道：&ldquo;冷冷冷！殘酷而漫長的寒潮可能打破所有記錄。全球變暖出了什麼問題？&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n特朗普的推特是什麼意思？其實特朗普的言外之意是：全球變暖是個騙局，他退出《巴黎氣候協定》是正確的。<br />\n<br />\n眾所周知，全球變暖是共識。然而，特朗普反其道而行之。他多次聲稱全球變暖是騙局。自2011年以來，他在推特上發表的氣候相關言論已經超過100條。早在2012年，特朗普便在推特上表示&ldquo;紐約正在下雪，好冷，我們需要全球變暖&rdquo;。一年之後，他又在洛杉磯喊冷，指責全球變暖是徹頭徹尾的騙局。這樣的言論一直延續到2017年6月1日，特朗普在這天宣布退出《巴黎氣候協定》。此後，為證明自己退出《巴黎氣候協定》是正確的，特朗普又繼續抨擊全球變暖。<br />\n<br />\n對於特朗普的此種說法，《紐約時報》曾表示，總統先生怕是沒有分清&ldquo;氣候&rdquo;和&ldquo;天氣&rdquo;的差別。雖然東海岸部分地區在新年前夕的低溫可能會打破紀錄，但當地天氣並不能代表氣候。為了讓商人出生的特朗普能夠更明白，《紐約時報》用了這樣一個類比：&ldquo;天氣&rdquo;相當於這一天你兜里揣的錢，而&ldquo;氣候&rdquo;則是你的淨資產，是長時間的總和。<br />\n<br />\n其實是《紐約時報》多心了，特朗普作為商業大亨，又當上美國總統，他不傻，反而聰明著，絕對不會連天氣和氣候的定義都分不清。特朗普想要的是&ldquo;美國優先&rdquo;，這一切在他退出《巴黎氣候協定》時就說得很清楚了。<br />\n<br />\n《巴黎氣候協定》規定參與國提交各自應對溫室氣體排放計劃，然後定期評估進展並相互敦促。奧巴馬政府承諾到2025年將溫室氣體排放量減少到低於2005年排放量26%至28%，並承諾在2020年前向較貧困國家捐助30億美元。<br />\n<br />\n特朗普認為這一協定是&ldquo;糟糕交易&rdquo;，奧巴馬政府談判工作做得很差，在絕望下簽署該協定。這損害美國人民的利益，如繼續留在《巴黎氣候協定》內，到2025年美國將流失大量就業崗位。<br />\n<br />\n簡單的說，既要減排又要出錢，這是特朗普對《巴黎氣候協定》最不滿的原因。何況，特朗普一貫強調&ldquo;美國優先&rdquo;，而&ldquo;美國優先&rdquo;說通俗些，就是&ldquo;美國祇能佔便宜不能吃虧&rdquo;。因此，特朗普可以睜眼說瞎話&mdash;&mdash;全球變暖是騙局！"},{"pid":"3cb384e17f8955c881218fda2113b626e8e78f3e","tid":913102,"uid":35430,"like":262,"dislike":39,"score":223,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T07:29:50.000Z","msg":"唯一同侵持相反立場<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61ad9fc97176b7238f2a03d8d3f81626504093fb","tid":913102,"uid":44562,"like":65,"dislike":0,"score":65,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T07:33:58.000Z","msg":"正 ! 全球跟唔減排碳 , 快啲升多幾度喇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/ok.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"418c7bf1441c99abacdf79ba38017564ec76baa4","tid":913102,"uid":19527,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"quote":{"pid":"61ad9fc97176b7238f2a03d8d3f81626504093fb","tid":913102,"uid":44562,"like":65,"dislike":0,"score":65,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T07:33:58.000Z","msg":"正 ! 全球跟唔減排碳 , 快啲升多幾度喇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/ok.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T07:41:20.000Z","msg":"焦土<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96da202b144ab9963bb6153211aebabc259797a8","tid":913102,"uid":126283,"like":143,"dislike":4,"score":139,"quote":{"pid":"61ad9fc97176b7238f2a03d8d3f81626504093fb","tid":913102,"uid":44562,"like":65,"dislike":0,"score":65,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T07:33:58.000Z","msg":"正 ! 全球跟唔減排碳 , 快啲升多幾度喇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/ok.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T07:43:17.000Z","msg":"減完又點，轉頭支那又排埋你果份，又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c29fc3015377c309c993579ed9199dd014b2bbc9","tid":913102,"uid":126100,"like":91,"dislike":5,"score":86,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T07:49:42.000Z","msg":"trump &amp; 連登仔：一到冬天暖化撚死哂去邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c47e58632d0d9ea72b315ba2f602747ebbb4d11d","tid":913102,"uid":91813,"like":2,"dislike":7,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T08:20:26.000Z","msg":"trump就係聰明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21b4104471b649eef0d83f0b19071f389954b7ab","tid":913102,"uid":51828,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T08:33:50.000Z","msg":"最尾3段先係重點"},{"pid":"0ac490cc20fe4c67d418dbcc8ec1f4cdc72d4552","tid":913102,"uid":77196,"like":37,"dislike":0,"score":37,"quote":{"pid":"96da202b144ab9963bb6153211aebabc259797a8","tid":913102,"uid":126283,"like":143,"dislike":4,"score":139,"quote":{"pid":"61ad9fc97176b7238f2a03d8d3f81626504093fb","tid":913102,"uid":44562,"like":65,"dislike":0,"score":65,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T07:33:58.000Z","msg":"正 ! 全球跟唔減排碳 , 快啲升多幾度喇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/ok.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T07:43:17.000Z","msg":"減完又點，轉頭支那又排埋你果份，又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T08:38:14.000Z","msg":"要解決全球暖化問題，首先應該消滅鄰國先 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9d448caaf99ba0d6d80ce567e29880d5cfadd81","tid":913102,"uid":18395,"like":92,"dislike":1,"score":91,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T08:45:00.000Z","msg":"用香港黎講<br />\n以前12月點會著短袖T恤"},{"pid":"7e2cd27e52858a16f66cbdc12f1f6447cd1bf223","tid":913102,"uid":4942,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T09:07:10.000Z","msg":"中國簽了巴黎協議<br />\n<br />\n減排減左幾多？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad39ca256d57a17ae52b7d94f04a9ccfc16b5416","tid":913102,"uid":4942,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T09:11:32.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">2017年，中國排放了117億噸的溫室氣體，佔世界總量的四分之一。其中包括92億噸的二氧化碳，超過美國和歐盟的總和</span>，二氧化碳是加速氣候變化的主要原因。<br />\n報告稱，經過兩年的穩定運行，中國的二氧化碳排放量在2017年有所增加，先期估計增長率範圍在1.4%至4.1%。這主要是因為它燃燒了更多的煤炭，這是主要的排放源。<br />\n2017年之前，中國的煤炭消費和排放量已經趨於平緩，這為全球氣候變化政策的擁護者帶來了希望。這種增長抑制了一些樂觀情緒。<br />\n氣候和能源研究人員表示，一個國家的碳排放量是否達到峰值是無法在當時就弄清楚的，只有過幾年後才能出現明確的全貌。美國就是如此，直到前不久，美國還是世界上最大的二氧化碳排放國。據挪威一個研究小組稱，美國的排放量在2007年達到頂峰，然後才開始下降。"},{"pid":"40989564c14a7c9a5457747aed704dbde28fad88","tid":913102,"uid":4942,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T09:13:32.000Z","msg":"該報告由現在哥倫比亞大學任職的前美國能源官員戴維&middot;桑德羅(David Sandalow)撰寫，對2017年中國的排放和煤炭使用情況進行了廣泛研究，迄今為止，中國是世界上最大的加速氣候變化的溫室氣體排放國。該研究還分析了中國政府和共產黨最近關於氣候的政策舉措。<br />\n中國制定了廣泛的氣候政策，將其載入國家的五年計劃和省級與地方級的藍圖中。因此，報告稱，它正在實現其主要的氣候變化目標，包括一項降低碳強度的措施，令二氧化碳排放量在不遲於2030年達到峰值，到那一年，五分之一的能源將來自非化石燃料來源。<br />\n與此同時，<span style=\"color: red;\">該報告稱，如果中國的碳排放量繼續保持目前的速度，各國將更難實現重要的氣候變化政策目標&mdash;&mdash;最顯著的一項，是將全球平均溫度上升限制在高於前工業化水平3.6華氏度或2攝氏度之內。</span><br />\n<br />\n資料來源：紐約時報 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5951cc83a1d3f84df16f3ab9c813181a28aec116","tid":913102,"uid":109173,"like":3,"dislike":6,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T09:19:32.000Z","msg":"侵明撚狗，班友仲真心膠到以為佢唔撚識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a05fee541eea9919a21862a9505ec7d6d2193a2","tid":913102,"uid":35205,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"quote":{"pid":"7e2cd27e52858a16f66cbdc12f1f6447cd1bf223","tid":913102,"uid":4942,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T09:07:10.000Z","msg":"中國簽了巴黎協議<br />\n<br />\n減排減左幾多？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T09:31:33.000Z","msg":"話自己發展中國家呀<br />\n一時又變第二大經濟體<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/01/182430_125253f98076fb346163f7895f2152fd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F01%2F182430_125253f98076fb346163f7895f2152fd.jpg&h=bccb6fe0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"db9435abf5e32e4ff7357beee80b86303e681bb5","tid":913102,"uid":4672,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T10:05:55.000Z","msg":"夏天加入 冬天退出 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a56cdfeee75c10755a1da4036d15c5d9d2400d5","tid":913102,"uid":1991,"like":9,"dislike":4,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T10:06:47.000Z","msg":"Trump：冷冷冷～wow wowwwwwww～"},{"pid":"e1b2cac5bfb835b7a799f54012bfcf4241c21ff2","tid":913102,"uid":1